          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H \colon  f \sim  g]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0014.xml" title="Homotopy" addr="forest://erct/erct-0014" type="local">homotopy</fr:link> between two functions <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f,g\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex>. For any identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  x =y]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, we have an identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H x \cdot  \mathsf {act}_{g}\,p = \mathsf {act}_{f}\,p\cdot  Hy]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
 
   
